This repository contains a modified Windows-oriented derivative work.

Modifications in this repository include:
- Porting the project to a Windows desktop application using Tauri and React
- Adding a tray-based settings window and Windows Hello unlock flow
- Adding Windows startup integration and idle auto-lock behavior
- Adding release packaging for Windows installers

